{
  "id": "adv_card_ngs_08_01_short",
  "title": "伊吹渚 (Short)",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_way_night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "私をヒロインにした恋愛ゲーム……ですか？",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ゲーム会社の持ち込み企画で、星見プロのアイドルを\n使ったゲームを作ることになったんだよ",
      "startTime": 8.3333333652,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "それってもしかして……前に怜ちゃんを\nモデルに作ったゲームのことですか！？",
      "startTime": 14.1797965209,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "察しがいいな、正解だ。前回が好評だったみたいでな\n今回はその第二弾ってことらしい",
      "startTime": 22.3666672707,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "先方は「今回はぜひ伊吹さんに」と\nおっしゃっているんだが……どうだろう？",
      "startTime": 28.100000604,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "ぜひやらせて下さい！　私があのゲームの\nヒロインになれるなんて……とっても嬉しいです！",
      "startTime": 34.456644392,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "私、もう何回もプレイしてて……\n怜ちゃん、すっごく可愛いんですよね！",
      "startTime": 42.4899777253,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "一人で全部のエンドをクリアした後は、月ストの\nみんなに順番にプレイしてもらって、横で眺めてました",
      "startTime": 49.3233110587,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そういう楽しみ方もあるんだな\nみんな、どんな反応だったんだ？",
      "startTime": 56.800000604,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}